# Build-context excludes for deploy/Dockerfile.
#
# IMPORTANT: Docker reads .dockerignore from the build CONTEXT ROOT (this
# repo root, since deploy/Dockerfile + docker-compose.yml use the repo as
# context), NOT from deploy/. A copy in deploy/ is silently ignored.
#
# node_modules MUST be excluded: the image runs `bun install` on Linux, so
# host node_modules (Windows/macOS node-pty prebuilds) would otherwise be
# copied over the freshly-built Linux ones by `COPY . .` and break the
# daemon at runtime.
node_modules
**/node_modules
packages/ui/dist
artifacts
build
.git
.github
*.log
.DS_Store
